### ─── AUTH SERVICE ───────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Register Admin User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@sass.local",
  "password": "Admin@123",
  "firstName": "Arjun",
  "lastName": "Sharma",
  "role": "admin"
}

### 2. Login
# @name loginResponse
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@sass.local",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### (Save token from login response)
@accessToken = {{loginResponse.response.body.accessToken}}
@refreshToken = {{loginResponse.response.body.refreshToken}}

### 3. Get Current User
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4. Refresh Token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 5. Change Password
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "Admin@123",
  "newPassword": "Admin@456"
}

### 6. Logout
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### ─── EVENT SERVICE ──────────────────────────────────────

### 7. Get All Events
GET http://localhost:3000/api/events?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 8. Get Events with Filters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/events?type=intrusion&severity=critical&camera=CAM-01&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 9. Get Recent Events (Last 10 minutes)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/events/recent?minutes=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 10. Get Event Stats
GET http://localhost:3000/api/events/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 11. Get Event by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/events/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 12. Resolve Event
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/events/{{eventId}}/resolve
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 13. Create Zone
POST http://localhost:3000/api/zones
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Zone",
  "cameraId": "CAM-01",
  "type": "restricted",
  "coordinates": [[100,100],[400,100],[400,300],[100,300]]
}

### 14. Get All Zones
GET http://localhost:3000/api/zones
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ─── ALERT SERVICE ──────────────────────────────────────

### 15. Get Alert History
GET http://localhost:3000/api/alerts/history?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 16. Get Unacknowledged Alerts
GET http://localhost:3000/api/alerts/unacknowledged
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 17. Acknowledge Alert
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/alerts/{{alertId}}/acknowledge
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 18. Live Stats (active connections)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/alerts/stats/live
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ─── GENAI SERVICE ──────────────────────────────────────

### 19. Natural Language Query
# @name aiQuery
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ai/query
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Last 10 minutes mein kya hua?"
}

@aiConvId = {{aiQuery.response.body.conversationId}}

### 20. Follow-up Query (with conversation context)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ai/query
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Koi critical intrusion tha?",
  "conversationId": "{{aiConvId}}"
}

### 21. Query with Camera Filter
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ai/query
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "CAM-01 pe kya activity thi aaj?",
  "cameraId": "CAM-01"
}

### 22. Summarize Specific Event
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ai/summarize
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}"
}

### 23. Generate Shift Report
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ai/report
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shiftStart": "2024-01-15T09:00:00.000Z",
  "shiftEnd": "2024-01-15T17:00:00.000Z"
}

### 24. Get Conversation History
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ai/conversations/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 25. Delete Conversation
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/ai/conversations/{{aiConvId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ─── DETECTION SERVICE (Direct) ──────────────────────────

### 26. Detection Health Check
GET http://localhost:8001/health

### 27. Detection Stats
GET http://localhost:8001/stats

### 28. Update Zone Coordinates
POST http://localhost:8001/config
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "zone_coordinates": [[0,0],[640,0],[640,480],[0,480]]
}

### ─── HEALTH CHECKS ─────────────────────────────────────

### 29. API Gateway Health
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### 30. Auth Service Health (direct)
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### 31. Event Service Health (direct)
GET http://localhost:3002/health

### 32. Alert Service Health (direct)
GET http://localhost:3003/health

### 33. GenAI Service Health (direct)
GET http://localhost:3004/health
